@baseUrl = http://localhost:5101
@adminKey = xxxxx

### Health — Liveness
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Health — Readiness
GET {{baseUrl}}/ready

### Health — Readiness (alias)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/ready

###

# ── Admin — Books ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# All admin requests require X-Api-Key header.

### Admin Books — Register a PDF
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/books/register
X-Admin-Api-Key: {{adminKey}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="PlayerHandbook2014.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./PlayerHandbook2014.pdf
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="sourceName"

2014
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="version"

Edition2014
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="displayName"

PlayerHandbook 2014
------Boundary--

### Admin Books — List all books
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/books
X-Admin-Api-Key: {{adminKey}}

### Admin Books — Re-ingest book by ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/books/1/reingest
X-Admin-Api-Key: {{adminKey}}

### Admin Books — Extract book with LLM (fires Stage 1 in background)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/books/1/extract
X-Admin-Api-Key: {{adminKey}}

### Admin Books — List extracted JSON files for a book
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/books/1/extracted
X-Admin-Api-Key: {{adminKey}}

### Admin Books — Ingest from extracted JSON (fires Stage 2 in background)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/books/1/ingest-json
X-Admin-Api-Key: {{adminKey}}

### Admin Books — Delete a book record and all associated data
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/books/1
X-Admin-Api-Key: {{adminKey}}

###

# ── Retrieval ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# version: Edition2014 | Edition2024
# category: Spell | Monster | Class | Background | Item | Rule | Treasure | Encounter | Trap

### Retrieval — Public semantic search
GET {{baseUrl}}/retrieval/search?q=fireball&version=Edition2024&category=Spell&topK=5

### Retrieval — Diagnostic search (admin, includes scores and Qdrant point IDs)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/retrieval/search?q=fireball&version=Edition2024&category=Spell&topK=5
X-Api-Key: {{adminKey}}

###

# ── Observability ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# /metrics is unauthenticated and only available when OpenTelemetry:Enabled is true.

### Metrics — Prometheus scraping endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/metrics
